title: No. 23 Red Raiders prepared for Big 12 Championships - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 23 Red Raiders prepared for Big 12 Championships - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: Texas Tech will search for its first Big 12 title in school history this weekend when the No. 23 Red Raiders tee off at the conference tournament Friday morning from The Clubs at Houston Oaks.
